n and sends them in to save the virtuous but imprisoned opposition leader who is also critically ill and due for execution. Just when the team has performed a perfect rescue, the multinational does a deal with the vicious dictator leaving the mercenary band to escape under their own steam and exact revenge.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":2.277,"vote_count":276,"poster_path":"/mUbbYSH0r5VQODUdgPXB8zjIKgz.jpg","release_date":"1978-06-28","vote_average":6.839,"backdrop_path":"/V80nkacoTSOwbdSakHDq1EhDg9.jpg","original_title":"The Wild Geese","original_language":"en"},{"id":7278,"adult":false,"title":"Meet the Spartans","video":false,"overview":"The heroic Leonidas, armed with nothing but leather underwear and a cape, leads a ragtag group of thirteen Spartans to defend their homeland against the invading Persians (whose ranks include Ghost Rider, Rocky Balboa, the Transformers, and a hunchbacked Paris Hilton). No one is safe when the Spartans take on the biggest icons in pop culture!","genre_ids":[35,14],"popularity":3.2996,"vote_count":1810,"poster_path":"/DWQOjAPvM8Kk1Qp3Xq0zae0Z6w.jpg","release_date":"2008-01-24","vote_average":4.09,"backdrop_path":"/8D3dBwSoPSGWRusbTYS8oR1tAu9.jpg","original_title":"Meet the Spartans","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1431045","twitter_id":"deadpoolmovie","facebook_id":"DeadpoolMovie","wikidata_id":"Q19347291","instagram_id":"deadpoolmovie","metacritic_id":"movie/deadpool","mydramalist_id":"284670","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/deadpool"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"deadpoolmovie","facebook":"DeadpoolMovie","instagram":"deadpoolmovie"},"gdvg_id":148689,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2016-02-11T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_31