9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Deadpool | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The origin story of former Special Forces operative turned mercenary Wade Wilson, who, after being subjected to a rogue experiment that leaves him with accelerated healing powers, adopts the alter ego Deadpool. Armed with his new abilities and a dark, twisted sense of humor, Deadpool hunts down the man who nearly destroyed his life."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148689/deadpool"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Deadpool"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"The origin story of former Special Forces operative turned mercenary Wade Wilson, who, after being subjected to a rogue experiment that leaves him with accelerated healing powers, adopts the alter ego Deadpool. Armed with his new abilities and a dark, twisted sense of humor, Deadpool hunts down the man who nearly destroyed his life."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148689/deadpool"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3E53WEZJqP6aM84D8CckXx4pIHw.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Deadpool"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"The origin story of former Special Forces operative turned mercenary Wade Wilson, who, after being subjected to a rogue experiment that leaves him with accelerated healing powers, adopts the alter ego Deadpool. Armed with his new abilities and a dark, twisted sense of humor, Deadpool hunts down the man who nearly dest